    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\">Added</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>​<a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-37142\"><strong>LCD-37142</strong></a> <strong>- Toggle to Allow Shell Access For Contributors:</strong> Added a toggle on the Settings page which allows admins to grant or block shell access to contributors. This mitigates a potential security vulnerability since users with the contributor role will have access to secrets which admins set as not visible to contributors.</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-37732\" data-inline-card=\"\" data-card-data=\"\">LCD-37732</a> - Elasticsearch Version Update:</strong> Updated Elasticsearch to versions 8.13.4, enhancing search capabilities and ensuring greater system stability and performance.</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-37862\">LCD-37862</a> - Log Readability Improvements:</strong> Made improvements to the logs feature by adding line breaks to avoid lateral scrolling and increasing the readability of important JSON content, improving the overall user experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\">\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38376\">LCD-38376</a> - Incorrect Log Levels in CI Service: </strong>Addressed an issue where info messages were appearing as errors in the logs.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
